# Scope First

- BEFORE making any changes, explicitly state the 1–3 files you intend to modify.
- If a task requires modifying more than 3 files, YOU MUST break the task into smaller sub-tasks and complete them sequentially (one stage at a time).
- ALL changes must be applied using exact string replacement or diffs (no full file rewrites).
- This prevents broad, unmanageable changes and reduces token waste.
